3_1","focus":"2","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"能什么模样。你自己还不清楚吗？","id":88,"figure":"avg_npc_213_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"——但是说真的，你让我们所有人都失望了。","id":89,"figure":"avg_npc_213_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"你可以不是监正会的高层，可以不是改变国民院的那个人，但是，你至少该是我们的英雄，我们的临光。","id":90,"figure":"avg_npc_213_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"我不知道你离开城市是要去哪儿，但我得说——除了我以外，他们大都失望了。再让他们见到你，他们会巴不得杀了你的。","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_213_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_108","name2":"avg_npc_213_1","focus":"1","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"那他们打得过我吗？","id":93,"figure":"avg_npc_108"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_108","name2":"avg_npc_213_1","focus":"2","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"啧。","id":95,"figure":"avg_npc_213_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_108#3","name2":"avg_npc_213_1","focus":"1","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"我放弃了很多东西，托兰。","id":97,"figure":["avg_npc_108",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"......只是，我还是经常怀抱着一个不切实际的想法。","id":98,"figure":["avg_npc_108",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"他们应该还在某处。","id":99,"figure":["avg_npc_108",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_108#3","name2":"avg_npc_213_1#2","focus":"2","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......","id":101,"figure":["avg_npc_213_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_108","name2":"avg_npc_213_1#2","focus":"1","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"他是战争英雄的长子，他是我玛恩纳的兄弟，是家族最强大的骑士。","id":103,"figure":"avg_npc_108"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"而她......是卡西米尔最美的人，优雅，端庄，如同一颗宝石......","id":104,"figure":"avg_npc_108"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"他们曾是我眼中的天之骄子，他们不该就这么......了无音讯。","id":105,"figure":"avg_npc_108"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_108#3","name2":"avg_npc_213_1#2","focus":"1","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"十多年了。","id":107,"figure":["avg_npc_108",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛恩纳","text":"我一直在想这件事。","id":108,"fig